      :Else
          page←Clean'Control'Section Dread node  ⍝!!!! FIX FOR SEARCH !!!!
          ⍝page←⊃Words'Control'Section code
      :EndIf
      desc←#.HTMLInput.dtlb'Description'Section code
      title←('All '/⍨2≥⍴page),('Core '/⍨'('=⊃⌽page),⌽End page
